egrANr7F31N5gIN4oJxEkUIA&oe=66E1917C"}, {"file_name": "UpscaledDungeonOfNekros6.png", "id": "1895786643957754", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974817_1895786647291087_2489373001132714866_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CRSituK0r-QQ7kNvgFsNvde&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ANm1OV6g1kTIJ2RRoF8KwHm&oh=00_AYCxKpNjyVI5N2WamtH8UD2dPKpgD80nyt977V042_NGhA&oe=66E16591"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "HeroHiddenRealmsTitleCoverArt.png", "id": "3763628287026264", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974558_3763628290359597_6941369554397762485_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HGBrUifbXB8Q7kNvgGP7tzo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ANm1OV6g1kTIJ2RRoF8KwHm&oh=00_AYD-XenebiK8HS9JcezsiMQ1RpDcB12e7N-9ksfMywk8UQ&oe=66E1988A"}, "display_name": "Dungeon of Nekros", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This is a one level demo for the upcoming full game. \n\nYou're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms.", "short_description": "You're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms.